snippet.title: Last Labyrinth 2nd Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The second teaser trailer for VR Escape-the-Room adventure game Last Labyrinth, coming Spring 2019.
Players must work to escape a mansion full of hidden dangers with a mysterious girl, Katia, that appears before them.

*The Last Labyrinth Kickstarter promotion campaign is now live! From Jan 24 - Mar 25, get exclusive merchandise including Art Books, Early Bird sets and Play Party tickets etc. only available through Kickstarter rewards!
https://kck.st/2RJwl1O

Official Website: https://lastlabyrinth.jp/en
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LastLabyrinthEN
Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/LastLabyrinth/
